  "summary": "Out-of-bounds Write in OpenCV",
  "details": "OpenCV (Open Source Computer Vision Library) through 3.3 (corresponding to OpenCV-Python and OpenCV-Contrib-Python 3.3.0.9) has an out-of-bounds write error in the FillColorRow8 function in utils.cpp when reading an image file by using cv::imread.",
